imdb.plot outline: Thanks to our knowledge we'll go through little tips, very easy to use on different themes like the well being, the decoration, but must of all the Feng Shui. A lot of TV Shows about decoration and design exist already, but none about the Feng Shui. However the decoration without Feng Shui is not making sense, it's like the Yin without the Yang. Moreover, the rapidity concept with this short format of shows will help to understand quickly, e.g. doing 'Home Staging', on a furniture, or how to purify our home, or how to create a headboard with a small budget...

plot: Thanks to our knowledge we'll go through little tips, very easy to use on different themes like the well being, the decoration, but must of all the Feng Shui. A lot of TV Shows about decoration and design exist already, but none about the Feng Shui. However the decoration without Feng Shui is not making sense, it's like the Yin without the Yang. Moreover, the rapidity concept with this short format of shows will help to understand quickly, e.g. doing 'Home Staging', on a furniture, or how to purify our home, or how to create a headboard with a small budget...::Lane Forbes
